the news summary.

01:28.956 --> 01:31.625 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: That was part of
a busy morning
for the president-elect on
Twitter.

01:31.725 --> 01:36.396 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
