widespread use of
excessive force and racial bias
against blacks

01:59.086 --> 02:00.954 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and Latinos.

02:01.054 --> 02:05.258 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
U.S. Attorney General Loretta
Lynch announced
the assessment in Chicago after
a year-long

02:05.359 --> 02:07.227 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
probe.

02:07.327 --> 02:09.262 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LORETTA LYNCH, U.S. Attorney
General: Our
investigation found that this
pattern of practice

02:09.363 --> 02:15.202 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is in no small part the result
of severely
deficient training procedures
and accountability

02:15.302 --> 02:17.137 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
systems.

02:17.237 --> 02:21.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
