force could
have been avoided altogether.

02:26.046 --> 02:30.951 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Chicago Mayor
Rahm Emanuel
called the findings sobering and
he pledged

02:31.051 --> 02:32.853 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
new reforms.

02:32.953 --> 02:36.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: U.S. Marines may
finally get
help after drinking tainted
water at Camp

02:36.223 --> 02:37.791 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Lejeune.

02:37.891 --> 02:41.328 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
