pay $1 billion
in fines and restitution.

03:07.187 --> 03:10.090 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Federal prosecutors announced
the plea deal
in Detroit.

03:10.190 --> 03:15.429 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they said three former
Takata executives
have been indicted for a
cover-up going back

03:15.529 --> 03:17.330 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
to 2000.

03:17.431 --> 03:20.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA MCQUADE, U.S. Attorney:
They signed
and submitted false reports of
test data to

03:20.567 --> 03:26.139 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
their customers, and they
directed engineers
to falsify and manipulate data.

03:26.239 --> 03:31.244 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Even after the inflators began
to fail in
the field and injuries and
deaths were occurring,

03:31.344 --> 03:36.216 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
these Takata executives
continued to withhold
the true data from its
customers.

03:36.316 --> 03:39.953 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The defective
inflators can
explode with too much force.

03:40.053 --> 03:44.024 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They are blamed for 16 deaths
and 180 injuries
worldwide.

03:44.124 --> 03:48.228 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: Today, the House
followed the
Senate in setting the stage for
repealing

03:48.328 --> 03:50.130 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Obamacare.

03:50.230 --> 03:53.667 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
