allows big
parts of the law to be removed
with a simple

03:53.767 --> 03:55.569 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
majority in the Senate.

03:55.669 --> 03:59.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Republican majority still
has not agreed
on their long-promised
replacement for the

03:59.239 --> 04:02.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
program, which provides health
insurance for
millions.

04:02.109 --> 04:06.079 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And Wall Street
had a fairly
quiet Friday the 13th.

04:06.179 --> 04:10.750 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
