President-Elect: I have
these guys, torture doesn't
work.

05:14.447 --> 05:16.449 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Believe me, it works, OK?

05:16.550 --> 05:19.085 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
