illegal to use
water-boarding or any other form
of torture

05:42.943 --> 05:48.081 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in the United States by our
military and by
all our other departments and
agencies.

05:48.181 --> 05:52.552 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
STEVE INSKEEP: Sessions
effectively committed
himself to telling the president
the U.S.

05:52.652 --> 05:53.920 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
