book on the presidency.

05:55.956 --> 05:57.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ELAINE KAMARCK, Former Senior
Adviser to Former
Vice President Al Gore: This is
the United

05:58.024 --> 06:03.697 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
States Senate reminding
president-elect Trump
that there is a Constitution,
and the Constitution

06:03.797 --> 06:09.636 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
has divided powers in it, and
that we are
a government of laws, not men.

06:09.736 --> 06:15.242 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: A president can
override the
attorney general, but it can be
politically

06:15.342 --> 06:17.043 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
