attorney general,
John Ashcroft, rejected a secret
wiretapping

06:28.388 --> 06:30.290 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
program.

06:30.390 --> 06:34.294 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This week, senators are asking
nominees if
they're ready to push back
against the president's

06:34.394 --> 06:35.595 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
