this alone.

07:42.662 --> 07:46.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEVE INSKEEP: This afternoon,
the president-elect
said he's not concerned about
these different

07:46.366 --> 07:47.467 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
