22:38.057 --> 22:42.428 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARGARET WARNER: He also
believes the apparent
trade-off, making the U.S.
reluctant to enter

22:42.528 --> 22:46.832 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the fray in Syria, where Iran
was helping
Assad, wasn't worth it.

22:46.932 --> 22:51.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHADI HAMID: In the Middle East,
we have learned
everything is interconnected,
and if we do

22:51.604 --> 22:55.874 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one thing in one area, it can
come at the
cost of something else.

22:55.975 --> 23:00.679 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARGARET WARNER: One week from
today, dealing
with that web of conflicts will
fall to a

23:00.779 --> 23:03.015 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
