23:03.115 --> 23:05.784 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm
Margaret Warner.

23:05.884 --> 23:10.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: For more on this
