let's focus on
three countries.

24:05.210 --> 24:07.079 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
General Petraeus, to you first.

24:07.179 --> 24:12.751 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Iraq, how do you size up the
legacy of this
president, President Obama, in
Iraq?

24:12.851 --> 24:14.219 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GEN.

24:14.320 --> 24:16.188 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAVID PETRAEUS (RET.), Former
CIA Director:
I think it's mixed.

24:16.288 --> 24:21.026 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
