25:00.933 --> 25:03.502 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ambassador
Edelman, how do
you see the president's legacy
in Iraq?

25:03.602 --> 25:04.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ERIC EDELMAN, Former State
Department and
Defense Department Official: I
see it largely

25:04.903 --> 25:06.772 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
