25:06.872 --> 25:14.213 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When General Petraeus and our
mutual colleague
Ambassador Ryan Crocker
negotiated the agreement

25:14.313 --> 25:19.451 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
