anticipated there
would be a residual U.S. force
staying after

25:19.551 --> 25:22.421 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
December 31, 2011.

25:22.521 --> 25:26.992 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
