residual force
there.

25:30.262 --> 25:32.097 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And was that a
mistake?

25:32.197 --> 25:33.332 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PHILIP GORDON, Former U.S.
Assistant Secretary
of State: Well, I think you have
to remember

25:33.432 --> 25:34.700 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
