25:34.800 --> 25:37.403 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
On balance, would it have been
nice to have
a residual force?

25:37.503 --> 25:39.071 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think the answer is yes.

25:39.171 --> 25:43.075 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It also happens to be the case
that the Iraqis
very much wanted us to leave.

25:43.175 --> 25:48.680 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Bush administration had
agreed that we
would leave by 2011, U.S. forces
shall leave

25:48.781 --> 25:50.582 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the country.

25:50.682 --> 25:53.552 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
