26:09.134 --> 26:12.671 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In that sense, one, it's kind of
a moot point
whether it would have been nice,
because it

26:12.771 --> 26:14.573 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
wasn't possible.

26:14.673 --> 26:19.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, two, I doubt, even though I
would have
rather seen some forces, that
even a residual

26:19.144 --> 26:25.317 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
U.S. force, 5,000, 10,000, would
have been
enough to stop the very powerful
trends that

26:25.417 --> 26:30.189 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
