of sectarianism,
the rise of ISIS which was
emerging from Syria,

26:30.289 --> 26:32.191 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
and all sorts of other things.

26:32.291 --> 26:35.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, yes, it would have been
nice, but we should
remember the context in which
the president...

26:35.327 --> 26:36.228 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
