ironies, the terrible
ironies of a country that has
suffered so

26:51.643 --> 26:53.178 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

26:53.278 --> 26:54.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: You want to
button this up
before we turn to another
country?

26:54.880 --> 26:57.382 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ERIC EDELMAN: Well, General
Petraeus made
the point I was going to make.

26:57.483 --> 27:03.522 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
