president did,
has done in Afghanistan?

27:23.308 --> 27:25.844 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PHILIP GORDON: On Iraq, General
Petraeus said
mixed.

27:25.944 --> 27:29.448 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
