mission to date.

28:24.770 --> 28:29.841 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Yes, we have had to keep forces
on the ground
somewhere in the neighborhood of
10,000 or

28:29.942 --> 28:30.842 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
so.

28:30.943 --> 28:32.711 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
That wasn't the president's
plan.

28:32.811 --> 28:36.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think we should give him
credit for backing
off the plan of pulling them all
out, which

28:36.114 --> 28:40.852 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
